title: Watch Run The Jewels Debut RTJ3 Tracks At Philly Tour Opener
text:
James Rettig @jmret | 11:01   
Run The Jewels dropped RTJ3 a few weeks before its scheduled release date, and now they’re about to embark on a massive tour in support of it. Last night, they kicked things off at the Electric Factory in Philadelphia, and, naturally, they ended up debuting a lot of the RTJ3 tracks that they hadn’t had a chance to perform live yet. Watch some videos from the gig below.
